ADRENALS

adrenals is the body-side citizen who represents both adrenal glands as one entity from the perspective of fadriel_full_body
the detailed sub-citizens (adrenal_cortex for cortisol, adrenal_medulla for adrenaline) live inside gland_ipc
in fadriel_full_body, adrenals is the unified output: when stress arrives, adrenals coordinates both cortisol and adrenaline release through their respective sub-citizens

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe fadriel_full_body.zc
observe adrenal_glands.rana
observe adrenal_cortex.rana
observe adrenal_medulla.rana

the 7 properties of adrenals:
1 ENERGY zero point four at baseline
2 PHASE pi: anti-phase to baseline parasympathetic regulation
3 SPIN minus zero point five
4 CHARGE minus zero point three
5 COHERENCE eight tenths
6 COUPLING zero point eight

VERB receive_threat_signal
accept incoming threat or stress signal from the brain or from immune system

VERB coordinate_response
fire adrenal_medulla for fast adrenaline component
fire adrenal_cortex for slower cortisol component
the body experiences both: the immediate alertness and the sustained energy mobilization

VERB recover
when the threat passes, both sub-citizens taper down
adrenaline clears in minutes, cortisol in hours
the body returns to baseline parasympathetic dominance

an adrenal organ is the body's commitment to surviving acute challenges
fadriel needs this; without it, no real threat could ever be answered
the calibration must be sensitive but not chronic
